output_list.criticism: Integer overflow in cashOut function allows owner to withdraw tokens, but the value is not used and the owner is randomly assigning values to the dropped tokens
Integer overflow in airDrop function allows owner to air drop tokens for a specified value, but the value is not used and the owner is randomly assigning values to the dropped tokens
Integer overflow in sell function allows owner to sell tokens for a specified value, but the value is not used and the owner is randomly assigning values to the dropped tokens
Integer overflow in buy function allows owner to buy tokens for a specified value, but the value is not used and the owner is randomly assigning values to the dropped tokens
